headline: Why Emerson Electric (EMR) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of engineering and automation solutions company Emerson (NYSE:EMR) jumped 5.4% in the afternoon session after an analyst at UBS upgraded the company's stock from 'Neutral' to 'Buy' and set a new price target of $168.
